        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Lee Kyeong-Do (Park Seo-Jun) works as a reporter in the entertainment department at the Dongwoon Daily News. He is an ordinary office worker who is neither rude or unusual. When he was 20, he met Seo Ji-Woo for the first time at a theater group club and they fell in love. She was his first love, but they ended up breaking up. When Lee Kyeong-Do was 28, they dated again, but broke up for the second time.\n\nNow, Lee Kyeong-Do works on a story involving Seo Ji-Woo's husband in a scandal. Due to the story, he reunites with Seo Ji-Woo after several years.",
